{
  "id": "adv_event_2203_01_01",
  "title": "その姿に憧れて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼、します……あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me… Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "優、すみれ、少し遅れてるわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ Sumire‚ you're a little late!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4,
      "endTime": 7.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！\n瑠依ちゃん、ライブの翌日なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!\nRui-chan‚ even though it's the day after the live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8,
      "endTime": 13.7161430904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、相変わらずタフやねえ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ you're always so tough‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9,
      "endTime": 17.2859863758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "（凄い、瑠依さん昨日ライブだったのに）\n（少しも疲れてない……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Wow‚ Rui-san had a live yesterday…)\n(She doesn't seem tired at all…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5,
      "endTime": 24.5420232875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "（……違う、疲れを見せない、んだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…No‚ she doesn't show her tiredness…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8666666667,
      "endTime": 29.407755057099997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱりあの人は別格……。トップを獲れる人……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She's truly exceptional… a person who can reach the top…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6,
      "endTime": 34.733333333400005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。雫ちゃんも今からレッスン？\n…………雫ちゃん、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. Shizuku-chan‚ are you going to have a lesson now?\n…Shizuku-chan‚ what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9333333333,
      "endTime": 45.4069515418,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 300.00000000000426
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ご、ごめん。気付かなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ s-sorry. I didn't notice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6333333333,
      "endTime": 49.1361677011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの練習を見てたんだね\n……圧倒されちゃうよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were watching TRINITYAiLE's practice‚ huh?\n…It's overwhelming‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3333333333,
      "endTime": 54.4178977364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "ん。凄いのは分かっていたけど……\n同じ場所に立つと、もっと実感する……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I knew they were amazing‚ but…\nWhen we stand in the same place‚ I feel it even more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5666666667,
      "endTime": 62.5997720046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "特に瑠依さん。才能だけじゃない。凄い努力……\n怖いくらい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially Rui-san. It's not just talent. It's incredible effort…\nIt's almost scary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8,
      "endTime": 69.98965961120001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "分かるよ。瑠依ちゃん、普段はあんなに優しいのに\nレッスンになると、先生より厳しいもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. Rui-chan is usually so kind‚ but…\nWhen it comes to lessons‚ she's stricter than the teacher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2666666667,
      "endTime": 79.25492710009999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリで勝てたのは奇跡……\n……今、勝てる気がしない。だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Winning the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix was a miracle…\n…Right now‚ I don't feel like I can win. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4333333333,
      "endTime": 89.07403251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私も、頑張らないと\n一人じゃない、サニピのみんなとなら……私でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to do my best too.\nI'm not alone. With everyone in Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2666666667,
      "endTime": 97.06228673800001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2666666667,
      "endTime": 98.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん、レッスン、しよう……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan‚ let's have a lesson…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.1666666667,
      "endTime": 102.0333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "うん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3,
      "endTime": 103.0979516657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……\nし、雫ちゃん、そろそろ一休みしない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa…\nSh-Shizuku-chan‚ shouldn't we take a break soon?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1666666667,
      "endTime": 112.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……\nでも、今のターン気になる、から\nもう一度……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa…\nBut‚ I'm curious about that turn I just did‚ so…\nOne more time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3333333333,
      "endTime": 120,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8099.9999999999945
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "今のは、軸足が一瞬ブレたから\n疲れているのよ。休んだ方がいいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The last one‚ your supporting foot wavered for a moment…\nYou're tired. You should rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2666666667,
      "endTime": 125.83681723689999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126,
      "endTime": 127.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、レッスン中に話し掛けて\nでも、怪我をしてほしくないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for interrupting during the lesson.\nBut I don't want you to get injured.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3,
      "endTime": 133.4279747775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "雫、レッスンは自分の体力と相談しながらよ\n頑張るのはいい。でも、焦ってはダメ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ during the lessons‚ consider your own stamina.\nIt's good to do your best‚ but don't rush.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6333333333,
      "endTime": 142.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "（兵藤雫……やっぱりこの子、凄く筋がいい）\n（普段は他のメンバーの陰に隠れて目立たないけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Shizuku Hyodo… This girl is really amazing after all…)\n(She usually hides in the shadows and doesn't stand out like the other members.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8,
      "endTime": 152.6333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、ありがとうございます……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes‚ thank you so much…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9666666667,
      "endTime": 156.9000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "おやおやライブの翌日に、鬼のように練習してる人が\n雫ちゃんのこと言えるんかなぁ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my‚ someone who practices like a demon the day after a live…\nCan she really say that about Shizuku-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.2333333333,
      "endTime": 165.0804335021,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 33.33333339998035
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 866.6666666999845
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ホントホント！　瑠依ちゃんこそ\nもうちょっと休んでほしいよね",
      "translations": {
